snippet.title: DX-Ball 2: 20th Anniversary Edition Announcement
snippet.description: The king of breakout games is back with a special 20th Anniversary Edition featuring new boards, online highscores, community editor and more! Coming to Steam Fall 2018.  https://store.steampowered.com/app/922400/DXBall_2_20th_Anniversary_Edition
